0-06-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620225526/https://www.weibo.com/2304129841/A0iDexZPd | dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}，最终票房号称超过了3亿元人民币，<ref>{{cite web|title=《天机：富春山居图》艺恩主页|url=http://m.entgroup.cn/593283/|access-date=2013-12-21|publisher=艺恩网|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817193149/http://m.entgroup.cn/593283/|archive-date=2014-08-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

